Interface EmbedDataSource

Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface EmbedDataSource
An EmbedDataSource is used to retrieve Embeds based on a unique name from various sources.

    • get

      Optional<Embed> get(String embed, Map<String,Object> placeholders, MessageResolver messageResolver)
      Retrieves an Embed based on the given name.
      Parameters:
      embed - the name of the embed to retrieve
      placeholders - a Map of placeholders to use
      messageResolver - the MessageResolver instance to use
      Returns:
      an Optional holding the Embed constructed from the retrieved embed json or an empty Optional if no embed was found for the given name
      Throws:
      ParsingException - If the embed json is incorrect
